      <title>克罗地亚计划对第二套住房征税以刺激预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/croatia-plans-to-tax-second-homes-to-bolster-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克罗地亚计划开始对第二套住房（例如亚得里亚海沿岸的度假出租房）征税，以增加预算收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/croatia-plans-to-tax-second-homes-to-bolster-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 16:22:24 GMT</pubDate>
