    <item>
      <title>英国要求房东提高房屋能源效率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/uk-to-require-landlords-to-boost-energy-efficiency-of-housing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国能源部长周一表示，英国将要求房东在本世纪末之前提高全国住宅的能源效率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/uk-to-require-landlords-to-boost-energy-efficiency-of-housing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 16:10:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国亿万富翁对巴尼耶的富人征税信号表示接受</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/french-billionaire-is-resigned-to-barnier-s-tax-the-rich-signal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国航运亿万富翁罗道夫·萨德 (Rodolphe Saade) 表示，他的公司准备缴纳更多税收来帮助修复法国紧张的公共财政，这表明该国一些最富有的公民可能正在对政府政策的转变产生顺从情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/french-billionaire-is-resigned-to-barnier-s-tax-the-rich-signal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 16:06:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗总统称他准备缓解与以色列的紧张关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/iran-s-president-says-he-s-prepared-to-ease-tensions-with-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗总统马苏德·佩泽什基安表示，只要伊朗看到对方做出同样程度的承诺，伊朗就准备缓和与以色列的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/iran-s-president-says-he-s-prepared-to-ease-tensions-with-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 15:56:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃尔多安将在与肖尔茨的会晤中争取 50 亿欧元的飞机交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/turkey-s-erdogan-to-press-for-eurofighter-jet-deal-in-meeting-with-scholz</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有迹象表明，北约两大盟国正试图改善关系，土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安正在敦促德国批准向土耳其出售欧洲台风战斗机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/turkey-s-erdogan-to-press-for-eurofighter-jet-deal-in-meeting-with-scholz</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 15:54:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯不断为普京的乌克兰战争提供资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/russia-budget-plans-show-no-let-up-in-putin-s-war-on-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯计划在2025年将国防开支维持在历史最高水平，并且由于总统普京对乌克兰的战争没有结束的迹象，未来两年国防开支只会略有下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/russia-budget-plans-show-no-let-up-in-putin-s-war-on-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 15:48:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Reeves 承诺将在英国投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/rachel-reeves-promises-real-ambition-in-uk-budget-next-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯暗示，她的计划可能会为气候转型和其他政府优先事项注入数十亿英镑的投资，她承诺将提供一份展现“真正雄心”的英国预算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/rachel-reeves-promises-real-ambition-in-uk-budget-next-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 11:35:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国联盟党将在行业谈判后考虑对汽车制造商提供援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/german-coalition-divided-on-car-sector-aid-before-industry-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国经济部长罗伯特·哈贝克表示，柏林执政联盟的三个党派将努力克服分歧，寻找方法帮助稳定该国陷入困境的汽车制造商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/german-coalition-divided-on-car-sector-aid-before-industry-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 11:01:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>诺斯罗普·格鲁曼公司计划在立陶宛生产弹药</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/northrop-grumman-plans-ammunition-production-line-in-lithuania</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的武器制造商之一诺斯罗普·格鲁曼公司希望帮助立陶宛建立一条弹药生产线，以加强这个波罗的海国家的国防工业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/northrop-grumman-plans-ammunition-production-line-in-lithuania</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 09:44:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列袭击黎巴嫩真主党，冲突升级，数百人丧生</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/israel-steps-up-attacks-on-hezbollah-targets-in-south-lebanon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当地政府称，以色列周一对黎巴嫩南部真主党目标发动空袭，造成 274 人死亡，双方敌对情绪不断升级，引发国际社会对爆发全面战争的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/israel-steps-up-attacks-on-hezbollah-targets-in-south-lebanon</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 06:01:15 GMT</pubDate>
